{"tid":926464,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"收集聖誕卡/信俾天琦","createTime":"2018-12-03T12:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T07:47:50.000Z","uid":12618,"like":41,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d76476fb1bfac2882db72e1de189d1200f679279","tid":926464,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"【聖誕卡及信件收集】<br />\n<br />\n步入12月，象徵即將又迎來另一年的聖誕。在一片歌舞昇平中，香港時局依然昏暗；普世歡騰，救主卻沒有降臨。<br />\n<br />\n救主未見，只有一位名叫梁天琦、靈魂赤誠的年輕人在三年前出現。梁天琦並非救世主，當時他仍只是一位生於壞時代的普通年輕人，分別在於 ── 他沒有坐困愁城，也沒有束手等待奇蹟，而是選擇站起來，開始拚搏。「既然沒有人能代表我們，那就由我們來代表自己」，只因一個簡單的念頭，他毅然親身參政，決心要將自己信奉的政治理念堂堂正正打進議會。往後日子裏，這位原本默默無聞的年輕人，把握每個機會讓人刮目相看。<br />\n<br />\n今日政治環境有如一溝絕望的死水，無力感瀰漫，使人灰心喪志。然而，在埋怨港人命途坎坷、不得眷顧之時，姑且毋忘我們至少擁有一眾肯犧牲、願意擔起香港命運的年輕人，包括梁天琦。漫長的重審已經展開，適逢強調感恩的節日，或許應當藉此時機執起筆，寫幾句話為天琦打打氣，告訴他一聲：我們依然銘記。<br />\n<br />\n【信箱地址】<br />\n郵政總局郵政信箱 8632 號 P.O. Box 8632, General Post Office<br />\n<br />\n【寫信須知】<br />\n聖誕卡寄送特別須知：<br />\n1. 卡片設計不可立體、附有任何電子零件、發聲零件、金粉、銀粉或彩粉<br />\n2. 卡上不可附有其他物件，如貼紙、郵票、剪報等，否則會被撕走<br />\n<br />\n普通信件寄送須知：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Eavyjm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Eavyjm&d=2k3wDdYGOcPuhK1JpPXsfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=957463b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Eavyjm</a><br />\n<br />\n【截收日期】<br />\n12月17日（星期一）<br />\n<br />\n相片鳴謝：  蕭雲<br />\n<br />\n#梁天琦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byHi92F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyHi92F.png&h=1ed46251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/172224869857024/posts/572924943120346/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F172224869857024%2Fposts%2F572924943120346%2F&d=2k3wDdYGOcPuhK1JpPXsfjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=bfe5015b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/172224869857024/posts/572924943120346/</a>"},{"pid":"0707b780d5e910cac8f83e11f641b2336054c612","tid":926464,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa027d20e17179f5039a23434331c41d54783ec7","tid":926464,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T12:45:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe535b0333f40e94a7175d69ba0061e88ddf8a3e","tid":926464,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩係到諗做啲手作仔嘅卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉頭就見到啲規限<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9124024cdd81608c665e2b3cbbc05bf94f2ace68","tid":926464,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"暴徒"},{"pid":"20590a022231f75fe986f0eb15cf150e459dc327","tid":926464,"uid":12618,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9124024cdd81608c665e2b3cbbc05bf94f2ace68","tid":926464,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:03:55.000Z","msg":"暴徒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"死撚開啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"de380c3d4364f53dac5cbf5280db320f7dbcb7a3","tid":926464,"uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe535b0333f40e94a7175d69ba0061e88ddf8a3e","tid":926464,"uid":178682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"岩岩係到諗做啲手作仔嘅卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 轉頭就見到啲規限<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:18:38.000Z","msg":"一張極普通既聖誕卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3c4c8adcdaad4c41a8cc0b34950074c3eb978d","tid":926464,"uid":77766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"2. 卡上不可附有其他物件，如貼紙、<span style=\"color: red;\">郵票</span>、剪報等，否則會被撕走<br />\n<br />\n郵票都唔得